BASELINE_VALIDATION.md

# Never send local, CI, registry, or cloud credentials to the builder. The
# Dockerfile also uses an explicit source allowlist, but excluding these from
# the context prevents accidental inclusion in cache/export metadata.
**/gha-creds-*.json
**/*credential*.json
**/*credentials*.json
**/*service-account*.json
**/*service_account*.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.git-credentials
**/.npmrc
**/.pypirc
**/*.key
**/*.pem
